    "description": "Meiho Holdings,Inc. engages in the construction and construction-related services, human resources related service, and nursing care businesses in Japan. It provides construction consulting services for public works, such as roads, rivers, and bridges to primarily national and local governments; and construction contract services related to roads and bridge facilities, roads maintenance, repair works and railway-related construction. The company also provides human resources services related to construction engineers and manufacturing staff, overseas outsourcing business, and security business to general contractors, manufacturers, facilities, construction companies; and outsourcing services, such as creating maps and drawings, data entry, and calculations, etc. for operations of domestic real estate and manufacturing companies. Its nursing care business include rehabilitation, hobbies and recreational activities, dementia care, flexible hours of use, and reasonably priced lunch services. Meiho Holdings,Inc. was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Gifu, Japan."
